-round. Watch Queue Queue. Watch Queue Queue  The track appeals to many walkers because it is more gradual than most of the alpine tracks around Arthur’s Pass village, and it does not climb above the bush line. COVID-19 Update: To limit the spread of the coronavirus, attractions may be closed or have partial closures. The alpine flowers are in bloom from November to February. This video is unavailable. <br>";s:7:"keyword";s:19:"bealey valley track";s:5:"links";s:2345:"<a href='https://www.pathshala.co/forum/page.php?id=d7382a-'></a>,
